      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RADIO RAMSGATE (2) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, holding on for a minor placing when second and beaten 2.75 lengths at this track over 300m in 17.58. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Top prospect. LARRGADI (1) filled a minor placing last start at Northam behind Neon Leon (17.80) in a LS6. Has the pace to be prominent. Expected to be in the finish again. ZATARA MAC (7) collided in the run and boxed on to place when a 3.5 lengths third (17.68) in a Grade 6 at this track. Worth another try. SWEETIE PIE (3) is in the mix after placing last time out.",
